  <h2>Using Frost Dates and GDD Together in Alberta</h2>

  <p>
    Frost sets the risk boundary. Growing degree days Alberta conditions provide determine development potential. Both must be evaluated together.
  </p>

<p class="muted">
  If you want a step-by-step overview of this framework,
